{"tid":330121,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"對我黎講 Linkin park先係真正音樂","createTime":"2017-07-21T02:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T17:24:26.000Z","uid":47996,"like":14,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"75e93827141a1f874957c90b428d6a2577ec9b63","tid":330121,"uid":47996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"由中學第一次聽in the end, bleed it out<br />\n到返兼職儲錢買企位聽live<br />\n直到13年睇第二次live 都係咁震撼<br />\nPut your hands up like this <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好正 好似將所有唔開心嘅野忘記哂咁<br />\n隨住佢地嘅音樂去發洩不滿<br />\n可惜已經冇機會再聽到chester把聲<br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅歌真係帶咗好多鼓勵同陪我渡過好多艱辛嘅時刻<br />\n仲記得第一次睇係同我個ex 此情此景不再<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每當有壓力嘅時候都會聽佢地嘅歌<br />\n冇咗chester嘅linkin park究竟會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nI dun know how I got this way<br />\nI know it's not alright<br />\nSo I'm breaking the HABIT TONIGHT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc70cffb79a78e964b65079b30c2ca479325fd6","tid":330121,"uid":62691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:07:23.000Z","msg":"自從轉左曲風後就開始少聽左&hellip; 剩狂Loop頭兩隻碟"},{"pid":"b017bd0e0de778969ecd178be20de0ece243ff64","tid":330121,"uid":69207,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:09:17.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 如果lp先係真正音樂既話<br />\n樓主應該冇聽音樂<br />\nRip樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b13503f8b6a49c46946bdf409202f1b1b1cd76","tid":330121,"uid":6211,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:12:40.000Z","msg":"onl9"},{"pid":"ce252fa4419fb267bb4813da5dff4f911a2f5cb0","tid":330121,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:21:36.000Z",